author: Susan Glaser, The Plain Dealer
title: Cracking down on four-legged fliers: Government may restrict airborne emotional-support animals
text: One Cleveland traveler reported seeing an unleashed German shepherd in a near-rumble with another dog - between the rows of the seats on her recent flight to Fort Myers.
